title: How To Spot A Fake iPhone
description: (   ) --- Today's Mystery Video -   This video features a knockoff of the iPhone 6s. It's actually quite similar in appearance and could probably sneak past the untrained eye. The software is an iOS lookalike skin on top of Android. This video identifies some of the key differences between a legit Apple iPhone 6s and a fake Apple iPhone 6s. Remember, if your App Store icon opens the Google Play store and you're using an iPhone, you're not using an iPhone.
